# Atlas-root working-tree cleanup (2026-07-06; chore commit retracted §A/§B of
# backlog ## Out-of-scope (explicit) ## Atlas-root working-tree dirty triage).
# `nul` line is defense in depth: the Windows-reserved-name on-disk file is
# un-deletable via Python `os.remove` / `shutil.rmtree` / `os.rename` on this
# build (PermissionError on the basename collision). The `.gitignore` pattern
# prevents any future reproduction from re-entering `git status --others`.
nul
script.py
repos/SynthSeg/
repos/report/

